quran[4{c,v,t}:
3,154,"is gham ke baad phir Allah ne tum mein se kuch logon par aisi itminan ki si haalat taari kar di ke woh avnghne lagey magar aik dosra giroh, jis ke liye saari ahmiyat bas apne mafaad hi ki thi, Allah ke mutaliq terhan terhan ke jahilana gumaan karne laga jo sara sar khilaaf haq thay yeh log ab kehte hain ke,"" is kaam ke chalanay mein hamara bhi koi hissa hai ?"" un se kaho"" ( kisi ka koi hissa nahi ) iss kaam ke saaray ikhtiyarat Allah ke haath mein hain"" darasal yeh log apne dilon mein jo baat chupaye hue hain ussay tum par zahir nahi karte un ka asal matlab yeh hai ke,"" agar ( qayadat ke ) ikhtiyarat mein hamara kuch hissa hota to yahan hum nah maaray jatay"" un se keh do ke,"" agar tum apne gharon mein bhi hotay to jin logon ki mout likhi hui thi woh khud apni qatal gaahon ki taraf nikal atay"" aur yeh maamla jo paish aaya, yeh to is liye tha ke jo kuch tumahray seenon mein posheeda hai Allah ussay aazma le aur jo khout tumahray dilon mein hai ussay chhant day, Allah dilon ka haal khoob jaanta hai"
3,155,"tum mein se jo log muqaabla ke din peeth phair gay thay unn ki a seen laghzish ka sabab yeh tha ke un ki baaz kamzoriyon ki wajah se shetan ne unn ke qadam dagmaga diye thay Allah ne inhen maaf kar diya, Allah bohat dar guzar karne wala aur Burdbar hai"
3,156,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, kafiroon ki si baatein nah karo jin ke Aziz o Iqareb agar kabhi safar par jatay hain ya jung mein shareek hotay hain ( aur wahan kisi haadsa se do chaar ho jatay hain ) to woh kehte hain ke agar woh hamaray paas hotay to nah maaray jatay aur nah qatal hotay Allah is qisam ki baton ko un ke dilon mein hasrat o andoh ka sabab bana deta hai, warna darasal maarny aur jalanay wala to Allah hi hai aur tumhari harkaat par wohi nigaran hai"
3,157,agar tum Allah ki raah mein maaray jao ya mar jao to Allah ki jo rehmat aur bakhshish tumahray hissa mein aeye gi woh unn saari cheezon se ziyada behtar hai jinhein yeh log jama karte hain
